@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: User Forgot Password

actor User
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Rate Limiter" as RL
database "Database (Neon)" as DB
participant "Email Service" as MAIL

User -> UI: Open 'Forgot password' page
User -> UI: Enter email + Submit
UI -> API: POST /auth/forgot-password

API -> RL: Check rate limit
RL --> API: Allowed / Blocked

alt Rate Limited
    API --> UI: 429 Too Many Requests
else Allowed
    API -> DB: Find user by email
    DB --> API: User found / not found

    opt User Found
        API -> API: Generate secure random token
        API -> API: Hash token (SHA-256)
        API -> DB: Save hashed token + expiry (10 min)
        API -> MAIL: Send reset link with raw token
        MAIL --> API: Email sent
    end

    note right of API
    Always return same response
    to prevent user enumeration
    end note

    API --> UI: 200 OK (If email exists, reset link sent)
    UI --> User: Show generic success message
end

@enduml